1
00:00:12,072 --> 00:00:15,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Uehara, I hope you're doing well.</i></font>

2
00:00:16,605 --> 00:00:21,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>It's already been two weeks
since we took that wonderful trip.</i></font>

3
00:00:22,105 --> 00:00:25,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I'll be 18 years old soon.</i></font>

4
00:00:25,705 --> 00:00:28,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>But, I hate to say it,</i></font>

5
00:00:28,472 --> 00:00:32,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I'm not sure if I'm prepared
to celebrate my birthday with you.</i></font>

6
00:00:33,005 --> 00:00:35,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>My good health was always
the one thing I've had going for me.</i></font>

7
00:00:36,405 --> 00:00:38,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>So, until yesterday,</i></font>

8
00:00:39,772 --> 00:00:42,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I never thought I'd end up like this.</i></font>

9
00:00:43,839 --> 00:00:45,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why didn't you answer?</font>

10
00:00:45,472 --> 00:00:46,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">ONE DAY EARLIER</font>

11
00:00:46,438 --> 00:00:48,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Answer what?
-My texts!</font>

12
00:00:48,638 --> 00:00:51,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yesterday and today,
you didn't answer any of them.</font>

13
00:00:53,638 --> 00:00:55,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But we see each other every day anyway.</font>

14
00:00:57,238 --> 00:00:59,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not the issue here!</font>

15
00:01:04,305 --> 00:01:05,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Look, Uehara!</font>

16
00:01:06,072 --> 00:01:08,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Check out these flowers
I saw near my work!"</font>

17
00:01:08,939 --> 00:01:11,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, they're so pretty, aren't they?</font>

18
00:01:11,538 --> 00:01:13,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Uehara!</font>

19
00:01:13,572 --> 00:01:15,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm at a cafe with Marina right now!</font>

20
00:01:15,472 --> 00:01:18,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yum! I'm having
a limited edition special cake!"</font>

21
00:01:18,772 --> 00:01:20,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was totally delicious!</font>

22
00:01:20,438 --> 00:01:22,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was so sweet! And really cute too!</font>

23
00:01:22,672 --> 00:01:25,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Those kinds of texts don't need an answer.</font>

24
00:01:27,105 --> 00:01:28,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, they do!</font>

25
00:01:29,271 --> 00:01:34,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the first person I wanted
to share my feelings with, that's all.</font>

26
00:01:34,572 --> 00:01:37,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, I understand. Is that all you wanted?</font>

27
00:01:39,972 --> 00:01:42,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've got the whole day off
from work today, right?</font>

28
00:01:42,772 --> 00:01:43,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

29
00:01:44,338 --> 00:01:47,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you think you've been at home
too much since you got this computer?</font>

30
00:01:48,039 --> 00:01:51,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a holiday today,
so why don't we go out somewhere?</font>

31
00:01:51,338 --> 00:01:54,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, but could you leave me alone?
You're distracting me.</font>

32
00:01:59,305 --> 00:02:00,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've been replaced.</font>

33
00:02:02,972 --> 00:02:05,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That computer means more to him than me.</font>

34
00:02:09,772 --> 00:02:12,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, but maybe</font>

35
00:02:12,271 --> 00:02:14,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was being too pushy.</font>

36
00:02:16,405 --> 00:02:20,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But that means
I'm a failure as a girlfriend!</font>

37
00:02:20,438 --> 00:02:21,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, dear!</font>

38
00:02:31,839 --> 00:02:34,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">These must be the DVDs Uehara rented.</font>

39
00:02:37,305 --> 00:02:40,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've never heard of any of these.</font>

40
00:02:52,371 --> 00:02:56,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you going to watch all those movies?</font>

41
00:02:56,138 --> 00:02:58,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, yeah.</font>

42
00:03:02,205 --> 00:03:05,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think I'd like to watch them with you.</font>

43
00:03:06,405 --> 00:03:07,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't force yourself.</font>

44
00:03:08,005 --> 00:03:10,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You only watch romances
and cartoons, right?</font>

45
00:03:11,305 --> 00:03:13,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not forcing myself.</font>

46
00:03:13,305 --> 00:03:16,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was just thinking I'd like to watch
your kind of movies.</font>

47
00:03:17,538 --> 00:03:18,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, sure, if you want.</font>

48
00:04:03,872 --> 00:04:05,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You want one?</font>

49
00:04:12,572 --> 00:04:15,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? It's not over yet.</font>

50
00:04:15,405 --> 00:04:18,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, but I'm going to watch it
in my room on my computer.</font>

51
00:04:18,205 --> 00:04:20,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Wait! Wait a second!</font>

52
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:23,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Leave me alone for a while.</font>

53
00:04:27,738 --> 00:04:28,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

54
00:04:33,738 --> 00:04:35,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I won't be outdone!</font>

55
00:04:35,772 --> 00:04:38,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My greatest weapon is my cooking!</font>

56
00:04:38,638 --> 00:04:39,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There we go.</font>

57
00:04:41,672 --> 00:04:42,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's all ready.</font>

58
00:04:44,338 --> 00:04:45,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

59
00:04:49,338 --> 00:04:52,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm going to be demure about this.</font>

60
00:04:56,805 --> 00:05:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know this is your day off
and I'm sorry to bother you,</font>

61
00:05:02,672 --> 00:05:04,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but dinner is ready!</font>

62
00:05:05,072 --> 00:05:06,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Send!</font>

63
00:05:18,371 --> 00:05:22,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess you're not answering
because you're angry?</font>

64
00:05:27,538 --> 00:05:29,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, that's right!
You're still watching that movie.</font>

65
00:05:29,805 --> 00:05:31,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry for bothering you.</font>

66
00:05:47,805 --> 00:05:49,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Buzz off! Leave me alone, would you?</i></font>

67
00:06:00,638 --> 00:06:02,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now I'm really pissed off!</font>

68
00:06:02,605 --> 00:06:04,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not letting you have a bite of this!</font>

69
00:06:04,972 --> 00:06:06,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll eat it all!</font>

70
00:06:08,105 --> 00:06:10,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go ahead and play with your computer.</font>

71
00:06:15,072 --> 00:06:18,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yum! This is good! Really good!</font>

72
00:06:19,072 --> 00:06:21,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And it made you sick.</font>

73
00:06:21,205 --> 00:06:23,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now you're hospitalized for three days.</font>

74
00:06:23,605 --> 00:06:27,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They think it was the oysters
in my seafood soup.</font>

75
00:06:27,271 --> 00:06:31,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Getting food poisoning from your own food.
That's so like you, Nao!</font>

76
00:06:31,171 --> 00:06:32,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, dear!</font>

77
00:06:32,572 --> 00:06:35,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And you two seemed
so lovey-dovey on that trip.</font>

78
00:06:35,805 --> 00:06:39,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That night nothing happened
because you got a fever, right?</font>

79
00:06:39,572 --> 00:06:44,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, but the bonds between us
became stronger.</font>

80
00:06:45,605 --> 00:06:48,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I just can't get his attention
away from that computer.</font>

81
00:06:48,538 --> 00:06:51,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Romance is probably pretty low
on his list of priorities.</font>

82
00:06:51,538 --> 00:06:54,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But don't you think
saying "buzz off" is going too far?</font>

83
00:06:54,305 --> 00:06:57,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Is that what you say to your girlfriend?
-No, it's not.</font>

84
00:06:57,505 --> 00:07:00,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not only won't he come for a visit,
he doesn't even answer my texts!</font>

85
00:07:00,672 --> 00:07:03,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's probably living it up
all by himself now--</font>

86
00:07:04,005 --> 00:07:05,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This could be a good thing!</font>

87
00:07:06,438 --> 00:07:07,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-A good thing?
-Yeah!</font>

88
00:07:07,738 --> 00:07:11,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It'll be good for him to realize
how important you are to him.</font>

89
00:07:11,472 --> 00:07:15,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They say,
"Absence makes the heart grow fonder."</font>

90
00:07:15,738 --> 00:07:19,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You get out the day after tomorrow,
and that's your birthday, right?</font>

91
00:07:19,839 --> 00:07:22,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You two will be totally lovey-dovey
when you get home.</font>

92
00:07:23,138 --> 00:07:26,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sure he's forgotten.</font>

93
00:07:26,105 --> 00:07:30,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. I bet right now he's wondering
what kind of present he should get you.</font>

94
00:07:30,705 --> 00:07:34,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saturday is his day off, so he might even
set up a surprise for you!</font>

95
00:07:34,371 --> 00:07:35,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, my god!</font>

96
00:07:36,271 --> 00:07:39,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A present from Uehara?</font>

97
00:07:49,105 --> 00:07:52,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Happy birthday, Nao.</font>

98
00:07:53,772 --> 00:07:58,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you, Uehara.</font>

99
00:08:01,672 --> 00:08:06,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Next year, and the next,
and all the years after that,</font>

100
00:08:07,171 --> 00:08:08,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">let's always be together.</font>

101
00:08:20,839 --> 00:08:21,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

102
00:08:21,939 --> 00:08:24,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Forever, Nao.</font>

103
00:08:30,072 --> 00:08:34,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You just have to be patient
until the day after tomorrow.</font>

104
00:08:34,738 --> 00:08:35,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course.</font>

105
00:08:37,405 --> 00:08:39,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What's that?
-Huh?</font>

106
00:08:39,205 --> 00:08:41,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Let me see!
-Cut it out.</font>

107
00:08:41,538 --> 00:08:44,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Out of hospital</font>

108
00:09:09,805 --> 00:09:12,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Welcome! Water, Nao!</font>

109
00:09:12,638 --> 00:09:13,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. She's not here.</font>

110
00:09:14,005 --> 00:09:15,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Nao's not here today?</font>

111
00:09:16,005 --> 00:09:16,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. Sorry.</font>

112
00:09:17,039 --> 00:09:19,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the... I came here
because I wanted to see her pretty face.</font>

113
00:09:19,605 --> 00:09:21,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't act like that.
I'll give you free roast pork slices.</font>

114
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:23,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're so generous, Issei!</font>

115
00:09:23,972 --> 00:09:26,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao has become the face of our shop.</font>

116
00:09:26,238 --> 00:09:27,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, she hasn't!</font>

117
00:09:27,638 --> 00:09:28,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Without her around,</font>

118
00:09:28,672 --> 00:09:30,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">there's a lot less trouble
with broken bowls.</font>

119
00:09:30,872 --> 00:09:32,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm done.
-Get the register, Nao.</font>

120
00:09:33,805 --> 00:09:35,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. She's not here.</font>

121
00:09:35,605 --> 00:09:37,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">MEGUROGAOKA SAKURA HOSPITAL</font>

122
00:09:39,972 --> 00:09:41,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't take it.</font>

123
00:09:42,205 --> 00:09:43,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't take this anymore.</font>

124
00:09:44,638 --> 00:09:46,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

125
00:09:48,939 --> 00:09:50,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

126
00:09:53,005 --> 00:09:54,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

127
00:09:56,271 --> 00:09:57,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

128
00:09:58,705 --> 00:10:00,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, Uehara!</font>

129
00:10:02,872 --> 00:10:05,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh! Hello--
-<i>This is an answering service.</i></font>

130
00:10:05,905 --> 00:10:09,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara. This is Nao.</font>

131
00:10:09,705 --> 00:10:11,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You must be busy with work.</font>

132
00:10:11,338 --> 00:10:13,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm doing fine! Just fine!</font>

133
00:10:15,638 --> 00:10:19,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll be home the day after tomorrow,
no problem. Don't worry about me.</font>

134
00:10:19,271 --> 00:10:21,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't need to worry about me at all.
Really!</font>

135
00:10:21,605 --> 00:10:23,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't have to visit either--</font>

136
00:10:38,538 --> 00:10:40,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Such a cruel boyfriend.</font>

137
00:10:42,305 --> 00:10:45,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">His own girlfriend is sick.
How dare he not contact you?</font>

138
00:10:47,538 --> 00:10:49,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is none of your business!</font>

139
00:10:49,705 --> 00:10:53,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's... busy with his work.</font>

140
00:10:53,305 --> 00:10:55,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you sure he's working?</font>

141
00:10:57,438 --> 00:10:59,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, of course I am!</font>

142
00:10:59,705 --> 00:11:02,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Unlike me,
even though he's a high school student,</font>

143
00:11:02,171 --> 00:11:06,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">he's independent, gets great grades
and is good at sports.</font>

144
00:11:06,672 --> 00:11:09,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All that's pointless
if he doesn't treat his girlfriend right.</font>

145
00:11:09,972 --> 00:11:11,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But I'm the perfect boyfriend!
-Huh?</font>

146
00:11:11,872 --> 00:11:14,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm devoted and kind.
And mentally, I'm an adult.</font>

147
00:11:14,472 --> 00:11:17,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Plus, since I'm a university student,
I've got free time.</font>

148
00:11:17,805 --> 00:11:18,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I never asked.</font>

149
00:11:18,705 --> 00:11:20,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm Senzaki Yu. Nice to meet you, Nao.</font>

150
00:11:20,772 --> 00:11:21,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Leave me alone!</font>

151
00:11:21,905 --> 00:11:25,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought I was unlucky
to get acute gastritis,</font>

152
00:11:25,271 --> 00:11:27,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but it was actually good luck.</font>

153
00:11:27,105 --> 00:11:29,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was able to meet
this pretty little lady.</font>

154
00:11:31,072 --> 00:11:33,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Get your hands off of me!</font>

155
00:11:33,305 --> 00:11:35,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong with you?</font>

156
00:11:35,138 --> 00:11:37,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That hurt!</font>

157
00:11:38,305 --> 00:11:41,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's with that weirdo?</font>

158
00:11:43,072 --> 00:11:46,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wish I was with Uehara right now!</font>

159
00:11:48,238 --> 00:11:50,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>You don't need to worry about me at all.
Really!</i></font>

160
00:11:50,605 --> 00:11:52,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>You don't have to visit either--</i></font>

161
00:12:21,072 --> 00:12:22,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is braised beef with potatoes.</font>

162
00:12:22,772 --> 00:12:24,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I made more than we need,
so I wanted to share it.</font>

163
00:12:25,305 --> 00:12:27,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, thank you.</font>

164
00:12:28,672 --> 00:12:29,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">By the way, Uehara--</font>

165
00:12:29,772 --> 00:12:32,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara! You...</font>

166
00:12:32,939 --> 00:12:33,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not you again.</font>

167
00:12:34,039 --> 00:12:36,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is that any way to talk
to your best friend?</font>

168
00:12:36,072 --> 00:12:37,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're not best friends.</font>

169
00:12:37,805 --> 00:12:38,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And...</font>

170
00:12:39,572 --> 00:12:42,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you've got Nao, so why...</font>

171
00:12:42,705 --> 00:12:43,705
