223
00:15:10,205 --> 00:15:13,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The first time, he was totally starving,</font>

224
00:15:13,305 --> 00:15:14,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so he couldn't stop himself.</font>

225
00:15:15,738 --> 00:15:17,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Couldn't stop himself?</font>

