00:15:23,705 --> 00:15:24,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Darn him!</font>

231
00:15:26,371 --> 00:15:27,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>That spells trouble.</i></font>

232
00:15:28,472 --> 00:15:30,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You think so?
