233
00:15:32,238 --> 00:15:34,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, but you see,</font>

234
00:15:34,271 --> 00:15:35,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">she's got a boyfriend--</font>

235
00:15:35,905 --> 00:15:37,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Don't be a fool.
