265
00:17:20,805 --> 00:17:22,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A reunion?</font>

266
00:17:22,205 --> 00:17:24,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm in charge of organizing the girls.</font>

267
00:17:24,738 --> 00:17:29,171
