to get you to come.</font>

268
00:17:29,238 --> 00:17:31,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you think you can come?</font>

269
00:17:31,572 --> 00:17:33,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well... I've got work.</font>

270
00:17:34,005 --> 00:17:36,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please! Even just for an hour.</font>

271
00:17:38,171 --> 00:17:42,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess your girlfriend wouldn't be
