272
00:17:43,238 --> 00:17:44,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, it's OK.</font>

273
00:17:45,438 --> 00:17:49,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, you're still not over
what happened a long time ago?</font>

274
00:17:49,572 --> 00:17:51,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What happened a long time ago?</font>

275
00:17:51,638 --> 00:17:55,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know, I liked you the whole time
we were in school.</font>

