00:18:00,839 --> 00:18:03,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uhm...
-Yes?</font>

277
00:18:04,672 --> 00:18:06,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's your name again?</font>

278
00:18:08,505 --> 00:18:09,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm really sorry.</font>

279
