<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm terrible at remembering names.</font>

280
00:18:14,138 --> 00:18:16,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm Mami. Momoyama Mami.</font>

281
00:18:17,538 --> 00:18:21,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Momoyama... Mami.</font>

282
00:18:21,972 --> 00:18:25,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You snatched away the one person
