283
00:18:26,972 --> 00:18:27,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Momoyama Mami.</font>

284
00:18:29,405 --> 00:18:30,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's you?</font>

285
00:18:31,705 --> 00:18:33,371
