344
00:22:45,505 --> 00:22:49,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And why today of all days?</font>

345
00:22:52,772 --> 00:22:54,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My phone! My phone!</font>

346
00:23:00,305 --> 00:23:02,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>This is an answering service.</i></font>

347
00:23:03,138 --> 00:23:06,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Please leave your message after the tone.</i></font>

348
00:23:09,772 --> 00:23:12,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If he's going to do that,
then I'm going to his work!</font>

349
00:23:14,672 --> 00:23:16,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Eek!
-Whoa! You scared me!</font>

350
00:23:18,438 --> 00:23:20,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao! Here!</font>

351
00:23:20,872 --> 00:23:22,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? What's this?</font>

352
00:23:22,472 --> 00:23:24,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Happy birthday!
-Thank you!</font>

353
00:23:25,039 --> 00:23:29,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Happy birthday, Nao. Pretty huge, huh?</font>

354
00:23:29,238 --> 00:23:30,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Can you guess what it is?
-I don't know.</font>

355
00:23:31,005 --> 00:23:34,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>-♪ Happy birthday to you! ♪
-♪ Happy birthday to you! ♪</i></font>

356
00:23:35,105 --> 00:23:36,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Blow them out!
-Blow them out!</font>

357
00:23:41,738 --> 00:23:43,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Happy birthday!</font>

358
00:23:44,005 --> 00:23:45,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks, you guys!</font>

359
00:23:46,405 --> 00:23:48,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Are you surprised?
-Yeah, I sure am!</font>

360
00:23:48,672 --> 00:23:51,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We all decided to give you
a surprise party.</font>

361
00:23:54,072 --> 00:23:57,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I see. He tricked me.</font>

362
00:23:57,572 --> 00:24:00,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, Nao. Take a look at this.</font>

363
00:24:00,939 --> 00:24:04,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is what you've been wanting!</font>

364
00:24:07,572 --> 00:24:09,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Here goes!
-Have at it!</font>

365
00:24:12,772 --> 00:24:15,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara! Uehara!</font>

366
00:24:19,805 --> 00:24:20,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abe...</font>

367
00:24:21,005 --> 00:24:23,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Abe! Why are you sleeping?</font>

368
00:24:23,371 --> 00:24:26,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah! He's drooled on her present!</font>

369
00:24:26,205 --> 00:24:28,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dammit! What's wrong with you?</font>

370
00:24:29,171 --> 00:24:31,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here you go, Nao!
Exactly what you've wanted.</font>

371
00:24:31,438 --> 00:24:35,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A Moussy stole and a Tarepanda pillow.</font>

372
00:24:36,005 --> 00:24:38,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Thank you.
-Yeah!</font>

373
00:24:39,738 --> 00:24:42,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm really happy. Thank you, everyone.</font>

374
00:24:42,839 --> 00:24:44,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're welcome.</font>

375
00:24:44,805 --> 00:24:46,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-So, where's Uehara?
-Where's Uehara?</font>

376
00:24:48,638 --> 00:24:49,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Huh?</font>

377
00:24:52,638 --> 00:24:55,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You mean he still hasn't contacted you?</font>

378
00:24:58,839 --> 00:24:59,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

379
00:25:00,738 --> 00:25:02,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you saying</font>

380
00:25:02,405 --> 00:25:05,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">he didn't come to the hospital
or your birthday either?</font>

381
00:25:09,072 --> 00:25:10,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where are you going, Marina?</font>

382
00:25:11,072 --> 00:25:14,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't it obvious? Uehara's work.</font>

383
00:25:14,105 --> 00:25:16,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'll drag him back here if I have to.
-Don't be so hasty!</font>

384
00:25:16,371 --> 00:25:18,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't care what his excuse is.
This is awful!</font>

385
00:25:18,238 --> 00:25:21,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's her first birthday
since they started dating, and she's sick.</font>

386
00:25:21,271 --> 00:25:22,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is totally unacceptable!</font>

387
00:25:22,772 --> 00:25:25,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! Look! Look!</font>

388
00:25:25,839 --> 00:25:27,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I just got a text from him.
-Really?</font>

389
00:25:27,972 --> 00:25:31,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It says, "Sorry,
but I have to stay longer at work."</font>

390
00:25:31,638 --> 00:25:33,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He says we'll celebrate when he gets home.</font>

391
00:25:34,105 --> 00:25:35,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You sure you're not lying, Nao?</font>

392
00:25:36,005 --> 00:25:38,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah. I'm totally happy now!</font>

393
00:25:38,705 --> 00:25:41,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not just my friends,
but my boyfriend will celebrate with me.</font>

394
00:25:42,171 --> 00:25:43,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah!</font>

395
00:25:44,939 --> 00:25:47,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Let me see the text.
-Don't make her do that.</font>

396
00:25:47,472 --> 00:25:48,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm not lying.
-I think she is.</font>

397
00:25:49,039 --> 00:25:50,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Happy birthday, Nao!</font>

398
00:25:50,338 --> 00:25:52,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You're late, stupid!
-Happy birthday!</font>

399
00:25:52,605 --> 00:25:55,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is nothing to celebrate! Damn you!</font>

400
00:25:55,238 --> 00:25:56,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You drooled on the pillow!</font>

401
00:26:04,572 --> 00:26:05,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

402
00:26:07,905 --> 00:26:10,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Issei.</font>

403
00:26:10,472 --> 00:26:12,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you'd already gone home.</font>

404
00:26:12,572 --> 00:26:14,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I rang the doorbell.</font>

405
00:26:14,972 --> 00:26:18,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry. I didn't hear it at all.</font>

406
00:26:18,638 --> 00:26:20,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Did you forget something?
-Yeah.</font>

407
00:26:22,605 --> 00:26:25,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's something I forgot to say.</font>

408
00:26:26,738 --> 00:26:27,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

409
00:26:30,805 --> 00:26:32,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you happy with the way things are?</font>

410
00:26:34,605 --> 00:26:37,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you think there are other guys
that will treat you better than he does?</font>

411
00:26:41,772 --> 00:26:43,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-He treats me well.
-He does? But--</font>

412
00:26:44,005 --> 00:26:47,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara treats me very well.</font>

413
00:26:48,405 --> 00:26:49,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He really does.</font>

414
00:26:52,138 --> 00:26:55,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's just that right now
he wants to be alone.</font>

415
00:26:55,138 --> 00:26:57,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know how guys are like that sometimes.</font>

416
00:26:59,271 --> 00:27:01,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You mean he left?</font>

417
00:27:03,472 --> 00:27:06,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, it's nothing serious like that.</font>

418
00:27:06,105 --> 00:27:07,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

419
00:27:09,105 --> 00:27:10,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Tell me what's happened.</font>

420
00:27:20,839 --> 00:27:26,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's all because... I bug him too much.</font>

421
00:27:26,605 --> 00:27:27,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's that supposed to mean?</font>

422
00:27:30,305 --> 00:27:35,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Unlike me, he's very independent.</font>

423
00:27:35,738 --> 00:27:39,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's the type that likes
to watch movies alone.</font>

424
00:27:43,905 --> 00:27:46,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">With someone like me
around all the time...</font>

425
00:27:48,638 --> 00:27:52,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm just... a bother to him.</font>

426
00:27:58,371 --> 00:27:59,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But, you see...</font>

427
00:28:06,405 --> 00:28:08,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just wanted...</font>

428
00:28:12,705 --> 00:28:15,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">to share the same feelings with him.</font>

429
00:28:20,738 --> 00:28:25,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">To feel excited... or romantic...</font>

430
00:28:30,405 --> 00:28:36,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and all other kinds of feelings.
I just wanted to experience them together.</font>

431
00:28:51,205 --> 00:28:55,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wonder what it's like to share feelings
with the person you love.</font>

432
00:29:10,338 --> 00:29:12,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">COFFEE SHOP</font>

433
00:29:22,138 --> 00:29:22,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">YOSHIKAWA NAO</font>

434
00:29:35,338 --> 00:29:37,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abe told me that this is where you work.</font>

435
00:29:40,005 --> 00:29:43,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the hell is going on?
Why did you move out like that?</font>

436
00:29:43,738 --> 00:29:46,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It's none of your business.
-Yes it is.</font>

437
00:29:48,205 --> 00:29:50,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's not just an employee.</font>

438
00:29:50,572 --> 00:29:53,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's the face of our shop now.</font>

439
00:29:53,672 --> 00:29:55,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's like part of my family.</font>

440
00:29:55,905 --> 00:29:57,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't help but worry
about her emotional health.</font>

441
00:30:01,772 --> 00:30:06,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Or is there some other reason
why you've left?</font>

442
00:30:06,405 --> 00:30:07,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

443
00:30:09,672 --> 00:30:11,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abe told me all about you.</font>

444
00:30:12,538 --> 00:30:14,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've been pretty popular lately.</font>

445
00:30:14,638 --> 00:30:15,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

446
00:30:16,572 --> 00:30:18,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's some girl
bringing you home-cooked meals.</font>

447
00:30:20,672 --> 00:30:24,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you call that being popular,
then it's nothing new.</font>

448
00:30:26,905 --> 00:30:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How dare you brag like that?</font>

449
00:30:28,472 --> 00:30:31,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Chill out, man! Hands off!</font>

450
00:30:33,371 --> 00:30:35,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What's that?
-What?</font>

451
00:30:36,271 --> 00:30:37,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A love letter?</font>

452
00:30:39,271 --> 00:30:41,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who said you could look at that?</font>

453
00:30:52,039 --> 00:30:53,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So...</font>

454
00:30:56,572 --> 00:30:58,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">is this the reason you moved out?</font>

455
00:30:58,238 --> 00:31:00,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you ever see Yoshikawa Nao again,
I'll tell your school.</font>

456
00:31:22,105 --> 00:31:23,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Rice porridge.</font>

457
00:31:31,738 --> 00:31:33,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">MILK PUDDING</font>

458
00:31:38,939 --> 00:31:40,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara...</font>

459
00:31:45,338 --> 00:31:48,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When did you get this?</font>

460
00:31:49,472 --> 00:31:51,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The day Nao was hospitalized.</font>

461
00:31:52,205 --> 00:31:54,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A second one came yesterday.</font>

462
00:31:54,939 --> 00:31:57,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then how come you haven't told her?</font>

463
00:31:57,805 --> 00:32:01,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's ill, so I didn't want to cause her
any extra worry.</font>

464
00:32:01,638 --> 00:32:04,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But that's no reason
to move out all of a sudden.</font>

465
00:32:04,672 --> 00:32:06,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't know who's watching us.</font>

466
00:32:07,438 --> 00:32:11,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They could go nuts
and do something to Nao.</font>

467
00:32:13,371 --> 00:32:16,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wanted to think about what to do alone.</font>

468
00:32:19,939 --> 00:32:21,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How come you're like that?</font>

469
00:32:23,072 --> 00:32:23,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

470
00:32:24,839 --> 00:32:27,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao wants a relationship
with you that's equal.</font>

471
00:32:27,805 --> 00:32:31,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She wants to share everything with you,
the happy and sad things. Everything!</font>

472
00:32:35,271 --> 00:32:40,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you think you should be looking out
for her feelings most of all?</font>

473
00:32:45,805 --> 00:32:48,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Why do you have to make a big deal?
-What did you say?</font>

474
00:32:48,238 --> 00:32:49,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Anyway...</font>

475
00:32:50,672 --> 00:32:53,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm only staying away
until this blows over.</font>

476
00:32:54,072 --> 00:32:56,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Once things cool down,
I'll explain everything to her.</font>

477
00:32:56,538 --> 00:32:57,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You jerk!
-I told you--</font>

478
00:32:57,905 --> 00:32:59,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's the point unless you see her today?</font>

479
00:33:00,972 --> 00:33:01,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

480
00:33:02,039 --> 00:33:03,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">EVENING STAR RAMEN</font>

481
00:33:03,605 --> 00:33:04,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I was wondering,</i></font>

482
00:33:04,538 --> 00:33:08,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">do you think Uehara
doesn't know today is Nao's birthday?</font>

483
00:33:09,005 --> 00:33:09,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

484
00:33:17,338 --> 00:33:20,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No way! I'm sure Nao has told him.</font>

485
00:33:20,405 --> 00:33:21,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, yeah.</font>

486
00:33:21,405 --> 00:33:22,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no way he wouldn't know.</font>

487
00:33:22,905 --> 00:33:24,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, yeah.</font>

488
00:33:29,105 --> 00:33:30,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-He might not.
-You're right.</font>

489
00:33:37,238 --> 00:33:39,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks always. From Nao.</font>

490
00:33:43,705 --> 00:33:46,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I never knew it's your birthday today!</font>

491
00:33:46,905 --> 00:33:50,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not interested in anyone besides you,
Uehara.</font>

492
00:33:52,138 --> 00:33:55,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the most important person to me.</font>

493
00:34:05,505 --> 00:34:07,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What kind of present does she want?</font>

494
00:34:09,305 --> 00:34:11,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What kind of present does any woman want?</font>

495
00:34:19,939 --> 00:34:21,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Welcome.</font>

496
00:34:22,338 --> 00:34:23,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm looking for a birthday present.</font>

497
00:34:23,872 --> 00:34:26,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is our most popular item now.</font>

498
00:34:27,438 --> 00:34:28,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

499
00:34:30,572 --> 00:34:33,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I never should have bought that computer.</font>

500
00:34:34,839 --> 00:34:37,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm... could you</font>

501
00:34:37,905 --> 00:34:40,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">discount this for me?</font>

502
00:35:06,672 --> 00:35:09,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's rented some niche movies again.</font>

503
00:35:16,005 --> 00:35:17,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>LATE FALL IN MIRECOURT</i></font>

504
00:35:17,138 --> 00:35:18,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>MAGRITTE OF THE WIND AND CLOUDS</i></font>

505
00:35:19,138 --> 00:35:22,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He rented romances?</font>

506
00:35:28,939 --> 00:35:31,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are these for me?</font>

507
00:35:49,405 --> 00:35:50,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello?</font>

508
00:35:51,238 --> 00:35:53,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara! Where are you now?</font>

509
00:35:54,005 --> 00:35:55,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm right in front of you.</font>

510
00:35:55,105 --> 00:35:57,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK. I'll be there in a--</font>

511
00:35:58,472 --> 00:35:59,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

512
00:36:00,839 --> 00:36:01,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hi.</font>

513
00:36:04,872 --> 00:36:06,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara!</font>

514
00:36:07,005 --> 00:36:09,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you running away for?</font>

515
00:36:10,238 --> 00:36:11,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

516
00:36:13,405 --> 00:36:15,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got to tell you something.</font>

517
00:36:15,171 --> 00:36:17,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you ever see Yoshikawa Nao again,
I'll tell your school.</font>

518
00:36:17,371 --> 00:36:20,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What this means
is that someone is watching us.</font>

519
00:36:21,638 --> 00:36:25,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I thought
I probably should stay in my room.</font>

520
00:36:27,472 --> 00:36:30,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Why?
-Huh?</font>

521
00:36:31,805 --> 00:36:33,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why didn't you tell me?</font>

522
00:36:33,305 --> 00:36:35,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because I didn't want to
cause you unnecessary worry.</font>

523
00:36:35,371 --> 00:36:37,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not unnecessary!</font>

524
00:36:40,072 --> 00:36:42,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thinking about it together <i>is necessary.</i></font>

525
00:36:48,338 --> 00:36:49,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

526
00:36:54,738 --> 00:36:57,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This kind of thing
doesn't bother me at all.</font>

527
00:36:58,105 --> 00:37:03,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm used to your fans picking on me
and teasing me.</font>

528
00:37:03,338 --> 00:37:06,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But what if the school finds out?</font>

529
00:37:09,405 --> 00:37:11,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We'll think of something when it happens.</font>

530
00:37:11,738 --> 00:37:14,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It'll be too late once the trouble starts.</font>

531
00:37:18,005 --> 00:37:19,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You may be saying that now...</font>

532
00:37:25,305 --> 00:37:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but I know you like it better
when you're alone.</font>

533
00:37:33,005 --> 00:37:34,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

534
00:37:38,638 --> 00:37:39,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

535
00:37:43,338 --> 00:37:47,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong?
Are you sick at your stomach again?</font>

536
00:37:50,271 --> 00:37:53,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I can't take this.
-Huh?</font>

537
00:37:54,371 --> 00:37:56,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was so lonely!</font>

538
00:37:58,138 --> 00:38:02,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was worried the whole time,
and you never texted back to me.</font>

539
00:38:06,205 --> 00:38:08,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then when I finally
got out of the hospital,</font>

540
00:38:09,472 --> 00:38:12,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you had moved out. I don't want that!</font>

541
00:38:16,238 --> 00:38:18,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even if you do want me to "buzz off"...</font>

542
00:38:20,505 --> 00:38:22,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't want to leave you.</font>

543
00:38:25,405 --> 00:38:26,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry...</font>

544
00:38:29,572 --> 00:38:31,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">for sending you that text.</font>

545
00:38:35,238 --> 00:38:38,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't think I had put you
under so much pressure, Nao.</font>

546
00:38:43,538 --> 00:38:45,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But put up with this for now.</font>

547
00:38:46,605 --> 00:38:48,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There will be real trouble
if the school finds out.</font>

548
00:38:50,138 --> 00:38:51,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-We'll be apart only a little--
-No!</font>

549
00:38:52,171 --> 00:38:55,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It can't be helped! I miss you too!</font>

550
00:38:58,505 --> 00:38:59,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

551
00:39:01,205 --> 00:39:02,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

552
00:39:04,405 --> 00:39:05,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You really do?</font>

553
00:39:15,672 --> 00:39:16,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here.</font>

554
00:39:37,072 --> 00:39:38,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

555
00:39:39,171 --> 00:39:40,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't be angry.</font>

556
00:39:41,171 --> 00:39:44,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't have much money,
so this is all I could get.</font>

557
00:39:46,638 --> 00:39:48,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is mostly your fault anyway.</font>

558
00:39:48,805 --> 00:39:50,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why didn't you tell me
it was your birthday?</font>

559
00:39:55,605 --> 00:39:57,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

560
00:40:02,138 --> 00:40:04,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll treasure it forever.</font>

561
00:40:06,371 --> 00:40:08,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not <i>that special.</i></font>

562
00:40:21,939 --> 00:40:22,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

563
00:40:25,572 --> 00:40:26,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's go.</font>

564
00:40:27,872 --> 00:40:30,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Where?</font>

565
00:40:32,538 --> 00:40:36,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no need to go buy milk pudding
at this time of night.</font>

566
00:40:36,805 --> 00:40:39,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's your fault for eating mine.</font>

567
00:40:39,505 --> 00:40:43,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you'd gotten that for me too.</font>

568
00:40:43,638 --> 00:40:47,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! It's my birthday!
You should treat me nicer today!</font>

569
00:40:49,972 --> 00:40:51,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara?</font>

570
00:40:54,005 --> 00:40:55,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

571
00:40:58,405 --> 00:41:00,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's your special day, after all.</font>

572
00:41:01,238 --> 00:41:03,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, forget about it.</font>

573
00:41:03,939 --> 00:41:06,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm just glad you're back.</font>

574
00:41:19,338 --> 00:41:21,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How beautiful!</font>

575
00:41:23,171 --> 00:41:25,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a full moon today.</font>

576
00:41:25,872 --> 00:41:26,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

577
00:41:32,039 --> 00:41:35,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like they say,
"Absence makes the heart grow fonder."</font>

578
00:41:36,839 --> 00:41:37,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

579
00:41:39,738 --> 00:41:42,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We'll only be apart for a little while.</font>

580
00:41:45,705 --> 00:41:46,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You mean...</font>

581
00:41:53,105 --> 00:41:56,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's fight this blackmail, Uehara!</font>

582
00:41:59,872 --> 00:42:00,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You bet.</font>

583
00:42:12,205 --> 00:42:13,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

584
00:42:14,072 --> 00:42:15,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

585
00:42:17,271 --> 00:42:19,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you take me out here</font>

586
00:42:19,505 --> 00:42:23,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so you could show me this?</font>

587
00:42:24,105 --> 00:42:25,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No!</font>

588
00:42:37,105 --> 00:42:38,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so happy.</font>

589
00:42:39,672 --> 00:42:44,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, someone might be watching us.</font>

590
00:42:48,738 --> 00:42:50,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah, who cares?</font>

591
00:42:57,672 --> 00:42:58,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

592
00:43:00,872 --> 00:43:02,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

593
00:43:02,438 --> 00:43:04,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Happy birthday.</font>

594
00:43:07,772 --> 00:43:10,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you, Uehara.</font>

595
00:43:16,105 --> 00:43:17,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Mami!</i></font>

596
00:43:18,872 --> 00:43:21,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Yu! You got out of the hospital?</font>

597
00:43:21,905 --> 00:43:22,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

598
00:43:23,605 --> 00:43:25,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the heck are you doing out here?</font>

599
00:43:26,472 --> 00:43:28,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was just passing by.</font>

600
00:43:28,305 --> 00:43:30,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so sorry for not texting you back.</font>

601
00:43:30,138 --> 00:43:31,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, whatever. It's OK.</font>

602
00:43:38,872 --> 00:43:40,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Him again?</font>

603
00:43:46,972 --> 00:43:48,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so sleepy.</font>

604
00:43:49,472 --> 00:43:52,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I had never watched movies all night long.</font>

605
00:43:52,271 --> 00:43:55,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why did you watch all those DVDs
in one night?</font>

606
00:43:55,138 --> 00:43:57,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you were going to watch with me.</font>

607
00:43:57,672 --> 00:43:59,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No way. Romances are so boring.</font>

608
00:44:00,005 --> 00:44:02,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That still hasn't changed about you.</font>

609
00:44:03,805 --> 00:44:07,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, this is far enough. Get back inside.</font>

610
00:44:08,705 --> 00:44:09,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

611
00:44:10,205 --> 00:44:11,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's with you?</font>

612
00:44:11,905 --> 00:44:16,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But from now on,
you won't be home when I return.</font>

613
00:44:16,305 --> 00:44:19,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to make the most
of our time together.</font>

614
00:44:27,839 --> 00:44:29,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-By the way...
-Yes?</font>

615
00:44:29,572 --> 00:44:33,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why don't you ask Marina to come over
while I'm gone?</font>

616
00:44:33,472 --> 00:44:34,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why?</font>

617
00:44:34,371 --> 00:44:37,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, it's dangerous at night.</font>

618
00:44:37,972 --> 00:44:41,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And there's strange people
like that around.</font>

619
00:44:44,171 --> 00:44:46,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Quit staring, stupid.</font>

620
00:44:49,972 --> 00:44:51,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

621
00:44:51,605 --> 00:44:52,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

622
00:44:54,138 --> 00:44:57,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Issei? Is that you, Issei?</font>

623
00:44:57,805 --> 00:45:00,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-What are you doing?</font>

624
00:45:00,638 --> 00:45:05,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What happened to your face?
Are you all right?</font>

625
00:45:09,238 --> 00:45:11,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your dad found out
about the broken $12,000 bowls?</font>

626
00:45:12,238 --> 00:45:14,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah. The other day, that special customer</font>

627
00:45:14,572 --> 00:45:16,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">placed an order
for the first time in a long time.</font>

628
00:45:18,505 --> 00:45:19,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You idiot!</font>

629
00:45:21,039 --> 00:45:22,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't worry.</font>

630
00:45:22,839 --> 00:45:25,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was my fault for not telling him.</font>

631
00:45:26,171 --> 00:45:27,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What should we do?</font>

632
00:45:28,672 --> 00:45:30,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll go apologize to your dad.</font>

633
00:45:30,371 --> 00:45:31,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, don't do that.</font>

634
00:45:31,705 --> 00:45:35,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll tell him everything. You just wait.</font>

635
00:45:35,772 --> 00:45:38,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I can't just watch
without doing anything.</font>

636
00:45:38,839 --> 00:45:42,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't care what you do.
I've got to get to work.</font>

637
00:45:43,039 --> 00:45:45,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Cool as ice, just like always.</font>

638
00:45:47,972 --> 00:45:51,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. Could I stay here tonight?</font>

639
00:45:51,905 --> 00:45:54,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're going to be alone from today.
It's perfect timing.</font>

640
00:45:54,972 --> 00:45:55,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

641
00:45:58,472 --> 00:46:00,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If your boyfriend doesn't like it,
then I understand.</font>

642
00:46:05,438 --> 00:46:06,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, you can stay.</font>

643
00:46:07,138 --> 00:46:08,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-What?</font>

644
00:46:09,905 --> 00:46:12,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is really my fault
in the first place.</font>

645
00:46:12,805 --> 00:46:16,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can stay here for as long as it takes
for you and your dad work things out.</font>

646
00:46:16,839 --> 00:46:18,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, but,</font>

647
00:46:18,705 --> 00:46:20,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">morally, I don't think that's proper--</font>

648
00:46:20,672 --> 00:46:22,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't worry about it.</font>

649
00:46:22,238 --> 00:46:24,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're like family to me, Issei.</font>

650
00:46:24,738 --> 00:46:26,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's OK, isn't it, Uehara?</font>

651
00:46:28,538 --> 00:46:31,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you have any idea what you're saying?</font>

652
00:46:36,171 --> 00:46:39,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I won't be here starting today.</font>

653
00:46:40,572 --> 00:46:42,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know that.</font>

654
00:46:42,805 --> 00:46:44,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We just promised each other yesterday</font>

655
00:46:44,839 --> 00:46:46,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that we'd do our best
even though we're apart.</font>

656
00:46:54,105 --> 00:46:55,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-Don't you see?</font>

657
00:46:56,171 --> 00:46:58,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Since I won't be here...</font>

658
00:46:58,205 --> 00:46:59,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It'll be just me and you.</font>

659
00:47:01,205 --> 00:47:03,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! That's right!</font>

660
00:47:03,605 --> 00:47:06,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's right! That's no good!</font>

661
00:47:06,772 --> 00:47:08,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! I have an idea!</font>

662
00:47:08,772 --> 00:47:11,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You stay here too, Uehara.</font>

663
00:47:11,638 --> 00:47:12,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

664
00:47:12,605 --> 00:47:15,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Issei will be here too,
so it'll be like camouflage.</font>

665
00:47:15,072 --> 00:47:16,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Camouflage?</font>

666
00:47:16,805 --> 00:47:19,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come on, Uehara? OK?</font>

667
00:47:24,338 --> 00:47:26,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You sleep in the living room.</font>

668
00:47:29,238 --> 00:47:31,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you!</font>

669
00:47:33,438 --> 00:47:36,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! That's right!</font>

670
00:47:38,672 --> 00:47:42,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That means three of us
will be living together.</font>

671
00:47:44,538 --> 00:47:45,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You sure it's OK?</font>

672
00:47:47,538 --> 00:47:49,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It can't be helped.</font>

673
00:49:16,972 --> 00:49:19,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THIS IS A FICTIONAL DRAMA.</font>
